# ğŸ“˜ Divisibility Rules â€“ Number System

Divisibility rules help determine whether a number is divisible by another number **without performing division**.  

## ğŸ”¢ Divisibility Rules (1 to 12)

### âœ… Divisible by 1
**Rule:** Every number is divisible by 1.

